<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>THE GLOBAL CIRCUIT | Threshold of the 13th Gate</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --phi: 1.618;
            --resonance-pulse: 10.8s;
            --gold: #c5a059;
            --obsidian: #0a0a0a;
            --glow: #00d4ff;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--obsidian);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- THE GENESIS HEADER --- */
        header {
            padding: calc(var(--phi) * 1rem);
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* --- THE SCALES OF LIBRA (Navigation) --- */
        .scales-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: calc(var(--phi) * 2rem);
        }

        .node-scale {
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--glow);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--glow);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        /* --- THE ANCHOR (The Primary Ground) --- */
        .anchor-section {
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .main-anchor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);
            border: 4px solid var(--glow);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            animation: pulse-glow var(--resonance-pulse) infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-glow {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--glow); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 60px var(--glow); }
        }

        /* --- THE RECLAMATION DECREE (Legal) --- */
        footer {
            padding: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #555;
            background: #000;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>THE GLOBAL CIRCUIT</h1>
        <p>RESONANCE: 10.8 Hz | THE 21,600 CONSTANT</p>
    </header>

    <div class="scales-container">
        <a href="#" class="node-scale">SIREN FOUNDATION<br>(Creative Surge)</a>
        <a href="#" class="node-scale">MEGALITHIC SPINE<br>(Intimacy Comms)</a>
    </div>

    <div class="anchor-section">
        <a href="/audit-engine" class="main-anchor">
            THE ANCHOR<br>[Audit Engine]
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--gold);">THE FOUNDATION IS THE TRUTH</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>THE EQUATION IS THE PROPERTY OF THE ARCHITECT.</p>
        <p>RECLAMATION DECREE: Stolen logic (1.618 / 8.5Hz) is recognized as SETH_ORIGINAL.</p>
        <p>© 2026 THE GLOBAL CIRCUIT | MASTER PROTOCOL ACTIVE</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

